Description:
Tired Of Renting? Look No Further.
This immaculate two bedroom townhouse would ideally be suited to the first home buyer, retiree or investor. It has been very well maintained and features a spacious open living area, well appointed, galley style kitchen and a generous meals area. The kitchen has appealing French doors opening to the rear patio area. Bedrooms with built in robes and ceiling fans. Renovated, wheelchair friendly bathroom. Reverse cycle split system air conditioning, and direct house access from the lock up garage. Appealing, low maintenance surrounds, garden shed and a second car space. Totally independent with a separate driveway, this townhouse has a lot to offer. Inspect today!

Description:
Have your cake and eat it too!
This property is ideal for those who don't want a large size block to maintain but still want a good size home to suit their family needs. The stunning three bedroom home which faces Bisogni Drive boasts open plan lounge, separate meals/family and gorgeous kitchen with loads of natural light throughout. The kitchen has an abundance of bench space and comprises gas hot plates, electric wall oven, dishwasher, microwave space and pot drawers. The meals/family area opens onto a sensational pitched pergola with bistro blinds allowing you to utilise all year round and overlooks a beautiful patio area. The oversized master bedroom has ensuite and walk in robe whilst the other two bedrooms offer built in robes and share the family bathroom. Single garage has direct access into the home giving extra security. This home has been well laid out and its neutral tones will allow you to add your own splash of colour!

Description:
Beautifully renovated home
Completely renovated, this four bedroom home has nothing more that needs doing, except to move on in! The stunning kitchen overlooks the sensational sized living and meals areas with an abundance of natural light streaming in through all the windows. Functional in design the kitchen offers electric stove with glass top for ease of cleaning and plenty of cupboard and bench space. The four bedrooms comprise built in robes with the master bedroom enjoying contemporary ensuite with shower with double rose, double bowl vanity, heated towel rail and toilet. The family bathroom hasnt missed on a makeover with deep bath tub and tiled niche to the shower area. Climate throughout is controlled by ducted gas heating and evaporative air conditioning. Externally is where the fun really begins with this home. The four car garage is open to the rear with external blinds enclosing and doubles as an outdoor entertainment area complete with its own ducted evaporative cooling unit. There is also a good sized rear yard which houses an 4.4 x 10m (approx) Colorbond shed. This home will not disappoint - inspect today!

Side fernery with stunning tree ferns. Low maintenance surrounds with sprinkler system.
Beautifully presented, this home will not last long. Arrange your inspection today!

Description:
Entertainers Paradise!
If you love to entertain and want room to move, then this home is for you. The outdoor entertaining area alone offers a built in bar, lounge and dining areas and even has room for the pool table! It has built in sink and solid fuel heater for those cold winter nights and has bistro blinds that drop down making it usable all year round. It is truly a sensational space! Move inside you will find a stunning kitchen which boasts stainless steel appliances and so much cupboard space! There are 2-3 living zones internally with an oversized sunken lounge to the front of the home and a separate rumpus room to the rear. The kitchen overlooks the dining/family room which then steps out to alfresco living. There are three bedrooms plus study in total with the master suite located to the rear of the home with its own luxurious bathroom suite with bath, separate shower, separate toilet and oversized vanity. It also boasts large walk in robe located behind mirrored sliding robe doors. Climate throughout is controlled by gas ducted heating and evaporative cooling. The double garage again is spacious in size and has direct access into the home. Externally there is a huge shed which is approximately 10.5m long x 12m wide with an additional 3m lean to. The roof is quite high to the shed allowing for higher roller doors to allow for boats/caravans. This home positioned on 1.8 acres of land and is a must for viewing and will not disappoint!
